line_text: Most heathenish and most gross!
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Now here's another discontented paper,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Found in his pocket too; and this, it seems,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Roderigo meant to have sent this damned villain;
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: But that belike Iago in the interim
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Came in and satisfied him.
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: O the pernicious caitiff!
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: How came you, Cassio, by that handkerchief
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: That was my wife's?
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: I found it in my chamber:
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: And he himself confess'd but even now
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: That there he dropp'd it for a special purpose
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Which wrought to his desire.
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: O fool! fool! fool!
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: There is besides in Roderigo's letter,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: How he upbraids Iago, that he made him
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Brave me upon the watch; whereon it came
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: That I was cast: and even but now he spake,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: After long seeming dead, Iago hurt him,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Iago set him on.
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: You must forsake this room, and go with us:
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Your power and your command is taken off,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: And Cassio rules in Cyprus. For this slave,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: If there be any cunning cruelty
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: That can torment him much and hold him long,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: It shall be his. You shall close prisoner rest,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Till that the nature of your fault be known
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: To the Venetian state. Come, bring him away.
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Soft you; a word or two before you go.
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: I have done the state some service, and they know't.
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: No more of that. I pray you, in your letters,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: When you shall these unlucky deeds relate,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Speak of me as I am; nothing extenuate,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Nor set down aught in malice: then must you speak
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Of one that loved not wisely but too well;
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Of one not easily jealous, but being wrought
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Perplex'd in the extreme; of one whose hand,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Like the base Indian, threw a pearl away
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Richer than all his tribe; of one whose subdued eyes,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Albeit unused to the melting mood,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Drop tears as fast as the Arabian trees
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Their medicinal gum. Set you down this;
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: And say besides, that in Aleppo once,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Where a malignant and a turban'd Turk
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Beat a Venetian and traduced the state,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: I took by the throat the circumcised dog,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: And smote him, thus.
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: O bloody period!
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: All that's spoke is marr'd.
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: I kiss'd thee ere I kill'd thee: no way but this;
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Killing myself, to die upon a kiss.
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: This did I fear, but thought he had no weapon;
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: For he was great of heart.
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: More fell than anguish, hunger, or the sea!
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Look on the tragic loading of this bed;
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: This is thy work: the object poisons sight;
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Let it be hid. Gratiano, keep the house,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: And seize upon the fortunes of the Moor,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: For they succeed on you. To you, lord governor,
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Remains the censure of this hellish villain;
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: The time, the place, the torture: O, enforce it!
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: Myself will straight aboard: and to the state
play_title_long: The Tragedy of Othello, the Moor of Venice
scene_title: SCENE II.  A bedchamber in the castle: DESDEMONA in bed asleep; a light burning.

line_text: This heavy act with heavy heart relate.
